articles.description: Landry Shamet scored 16 points in just 23 minutes as No. 22 Wichita State cruised to a 95-74 win over UConn on Saturday night.
articles.headline: No. 22 Wichita State routs UConn 95-74

articles.description: His 3-pointer to beat No. 3 Purdue in a tense B1G matchup gave Miles Bridges and No. 4 Michigan State a signature victory and kept title hopes alive.
articles.headline: Miles Bridges rises to the moment for Michigan State
